    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Were the dive-bombers at Bir Hacheim shot down by anti-aircraft guns or by fighters?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-0b28a705-c870-49cb-927d-35aea2e6b5d0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
